-- Georgia - Atlanta
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'GA-ATL-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Grady EMS protocol: High-quality CPR, early defibrillation, ACLS medications. Consider ECMO transport.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Georgia - Atlanta Fulton DeKalb' AND c.state = 'Georgia' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'GA-ATL-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Stroke alert. FAST assessment. Last known well. Transport to comprehensive stroke center.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Georgia - Atlanta Fulton DeKalb' AND c.state = 'Georgia' LIMIT 1;
